              with colors alternating between the color specified by this p=
roperty and the color
              specified by the <code class=3D"argument">CrosshairColor</cod=
e> property.</p>
           =20
    <p>You can specify any color using an RGB triplet. An RGB triplet is a =
3-element row vector
        whose elements specify the intensities of the red, green, and blue =
components of the color.
        The intensities must be in the range [0, 1].</p>
